 it in healthcare technologies\nsuch as assistive robots to provide informed assistance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 19:13:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Aug 2020 23:15:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-01"}
