ely on the introduction of a new microlocal property for\n(pseudo)differential operators called $\\textit{operators of uniform divergence\ntype}$, and on perturbative arguments from spectral theory (especially on the\ntheory of Pollicott-Ruelle resonances in the Anosov case).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 20:16:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Oct 2020 14:23:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-20"}
