xtended TeV flux in the\nregion, suggesting that PSR J1809-1917 is indeed the counterpart to HESS/eHWC\nJ1809-193.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 20:32:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
