inear evolution. Nonlinear wake shoaling, essential for modeling wake-induced\nsediment transport and wake impact on the environment, is described well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Aug 2020 22:41:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
